To install "arsespyder" Web crawler, there are two methods available:

A) Installing from source code (RECOMMENDED)
------------------------------

   In order to install arsespyder from source code, next step should be followed:

   A.1) Install python-setuptools on your Linux distribution

   # apt-get install python-setuptools

   A.2) Download arsespyder from URL https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/a/arsespyder/arsespyder-0.0.3.tar.gz

NOTE: Alternative download URL is: http://sarroutbi.dyndns.org/DEVELOPMENT_TOOLS/arsespyder-0.0.3.tar.gz

   A.3) Unpack the source code:
  
   # tar zxvf arsespyder-0.0.3.tar.gz

   A.3) Install with "setuptools":

   # cd arsespyder-0.0.3

   A.4) Run python setup.py install, as root:

   # sudo python setup.py install

B) Installing binaries
----------------------

   In order to install from binary files, run "easy_install"

   # sudo easy_install arsespyder    
